程序包 org.janusgraph.diskstorage

接口 Entry

所有超级接口:
Comparable<StaticBuffer>, MetaAnnotated, StaticBuffer
所有已知实现类:
StaticArrayEntry
public interface Entry
extends StaticBuffer, MetaAnnotated
An entry is the primitive persistence unit used in the graph database storage backend.

An entry consists of a column and value both of which are general ByteBuffers. The value may be null but the column may not.

作者:
Matthias Bröcheler (me@matthiasb.com);
